title: JUN 24, 2022 - SUPREME COURT OVERTURNS ROE V. WADE
description:
In a massive victory for life, liberty, and love, Roe V. Wade has been overturned. Jack Posobiec discusses what this means for the new right, along with warnings of retaliations from various pro-choice organizations including Jane’s Revenge. A Pennsylvania drag queen is charges with 25 counts of child pornography – as conservatives we must speak out against the culture that continually enables the harming of our children. Flash Actor Ezra Miller, amidst controversies of child grooming, is housing a young mother and her children on a drug farm. And finally, a Philadelphia woman has her face set on fire, sustaining critical injuries, in a Kensington attack.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
